{
  "problem": "如果\n\\[f(n + 1) = (-1)^{n + 1} n - 2f(n)\\]\n对于 $n \\ge 1,$ 且 $f(1) = f(1986),$ 则\n\\[f(1) + f(2) + f(3) + \\dots + f(1985)\\]\n的值为？",
  "solution": "我们可以列出方程\n\\begin{align*}\nf(2) &= 1 - 2f(1), \\\\\nf(3) &= -2 - 2f(2), \\\\\nf(4) &= 3 - 2f(3), \\\\\nf(5) &= -4 - 2f(4), \\\\\n&\\dots, \\\\\nf(1985) &= -1984 - 2f(1984), \\\\\nf(1986) &= 1985 - 2f(1985)。\n\\end{align*}\n将这些方程相加，我们得到\n\\[f(2) + f(3) + \\dots + f(1986) = (1 - 2 + 3 - 4 + \\dots + 1983 - 1984 + 1985) - 2(f(1) + f(2) + \\dots + f(1985))。\\]\n要计算 \\(1 - 2 + 3 - 4 + \\dots + 1983 - 1984 + 1985\\)，我们可以将项配对：\n\\begin{align*}\n1 - 2 + 3 - 4 + \\dots + 1983 - 1984 + 1985 &= (1 - 2) + (3 - 4) + \\dots + (1983 - 1984) + 1985 \\\\\n&= (-1) + (-1) + \\dots + (-1) + 1985 \\\\\n&= -\\frac{1984}{2} + 1985 \\\\\n&= 993。\n\\end{align*}\n因此，\n\\[f(2) + f(3) + \\dots + f(1986) = 993 - 2(f(1) + f(2) + \\dots + f(1985))。\\]\n则\n\\[2f(1) + 3(f(2) + f(3) + \\dots + f(1985)) + f(1986) = 993。\\]\n由于 \\(f(1986) = f(1)\\)，\n\\[3(f(1) + f(2) + f(3) + \\dots + f(1985)) = 993。\\]\n因此，\n\\[f(1) + f(2) + f(3) + \\dots + f(1985) = \\boxed{331}。\\]",
